---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
    title="Services"
    description="Custom-coded, high-performance websites for local businesses. No bloat, just speed."
>
    <section class="py-24 sm:py-32">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl lg:text-center">
                <span
                    class="rounded-full outline-primary outline-2 px-3 py-1 text-sm/6 font-semibold text-primary"
                    >Services Offered
                </span>
                <h1
                    class="mt-6 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-pretty sm:text-5xl lg:text-balance"
                >
                    Professional Web Design & Development Services
                </h1>
                <p class="mt-6 text-lg/8 t">
                    Stop fighting your CMS and start winning on the web. We
                    build hand-coded, high-performance websites that load
                    instantly and score perfectly on every metric. No WordPress,
                    no bloat, and no security vulnerabilities—just clean, custom
                    code that scales as fast as you do.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-4xl">
                <dl
                    class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-y-16"
                >
                    <div class="relative pl-16">
                        <dt class="text-base/7 font-semibold">
                            <div
                                class="absolute top-0 left-0 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-accent"
                            >
                                <svg
                                    class="size-6 text-primary-content"
                                    fill="none"
                                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                    stroke-width="1.5"
                                    stroke="currentColor"
                                    aria-hidden="true"
                                    data-slot="icon"
                                >
                                    <path
                                        stroke-linecap="round"
                                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                                        d="M4.098 19.902a3.75 3.75 0 0 0 5.304 0l6.401-6.402M6.75 21A3.75 3.75 0 0 1 3 17.25V4.125C3 3.504 3.504 3 4.125 3h5.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v4.072M6.75 21a3.75 3.75 0 0 0 3.75-3.75V8.197M6.75 21h13.125c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125v-5.25c0-.621-.504-1.125-1.125-1.125h-4.072M10.5 8.197l2.88-2.88c.438-.439 1.15-.439 1.59 0l3.712 3.713c.44.44.44 1.152 0 1.59l-2.879 2.88M6.75 17.25h.008v.008H6.75v-.008Z"
                                    ></path>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            Bespoke Custom Design <span
                                class="text-base-content/75 font-light block"
                                >◦ Beyond templates</span
                            >
                        </dt>
                        <dd class="mt-2 text-base/7 t">
                            We don’t believe in 'one size fits all.' By
                            hand-coding every element from scratch, we build a
                            digital identity tailored specifically to your
                            brand’s goals. No restrictive themes or clumsy page
                            builders—just a pixel-perfect, high-conversion
                            interface designed to turn visitors into lifelong
                            customers.
                        </dd>
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative pl-16">
                        <dt class="text-base/7 font-semibold">
                            <div
                                class="absolute top-0 left-0 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-accent"
                            >
                                <svg
                                    class="size-6 text-primary-content"
                                    fill="none"
                                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                    stroke-width="1.5"
                                    stroke="currentColor"
                                    aria-hidden="true"
                                    data-slot="icon"
                                >
                                    <path
                                        stroke-linecap="round"
                                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                                        d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 0 1 3.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 0 0 3 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285Z"
                                    ></path>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            Ironclad Security & Hosting <span
                                class="text-base-content/75 font-light block"
                                >◦ Static architecture, total safety</span
                            >
                        </dt>
                        <dd class="mt-2 text-base/7 t">
                            Traditional WordPress sites are vulnerable to
                            database leaks and plugin hacks. Our sites are built
                            using a modern 'static' architecture that is
                            inherently secure. Combined with world-class edge
                            hosting, your site stays online, stays fast, and
                            remains virtually impossible to compromise—no server
                            maintenance required on your end.
                        </dd>
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative pl-16">
                        <dt class="text-base/7 font-semibold">
                            <div
                                class="absolute top-0 left-0 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-accent"
                            >
                                <svg
                                    class="size-6 text-primary-content"
                                    fill="none"
                                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                    stroke-width="1.5"
                                    stroke="currentColor"
                                    aria-hidden="true"
                                    data-slot="icon"
                                >
                                    <path
                                        stroke-linecap="round"
                                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                                        d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12c0 1.268-.63 2.39-1.593 3.068a3.745 3.745 0 0 1-1.043 3.296 3.745 3.745 0 0 1-3.296 1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 12 21c-1.268 0-2.39-.63-3.068-1.593a3.746 3.746 0 0 1-3.296-1.043 3.745 3.745 0 0 1-1.043-3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 3 12c0-1.268.63-2.39 1.593-3.068a3.745 3.745 0 0 1 1.043-3.296 3.746 3.746 0 0 1 3.296-1.043A3.746 3.746 0 0 1 12 3c1.268 0 2.39.63 3.068 1.593a3.746 3.746 0 0 1 3.296 1.043 3.746 3.746 0 0 1 1.043 3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 21 12Z"
                                    ></path>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            Perfect Performance Scores <span
                                class="text-base-content/75 font-light block"
                                >◦ 90+ Google Insights</span
                            >
                        </dt>
                        <dd class="mt-2 text-base/7 t">
                            Speed is a ranking factor. We guarantee elite
                            performance by removing the 'code bloat' that slows
                            down WordPress sites. Your visitors enjoy
                            near-instant load times, and you enjoy the SEO
                            benefits of perfect scores on Google PageSpeed
                            Insights. We don't just aim for green; we aim for
                            100.
                        </dd>
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative pl-16">
                        <dt class="text-base/7 font-semibold">
                            <div
                                class="absolute top-0 left-0 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-accent"
                            >
                                <svg
                                    class="size-6 text-primary-content"
                                    fill="none"
                                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                    stroke-width="1.5"
                                    stroke="currentColor"
                                    aria-hidden="true"
                                    data-slot="icon"
                                >
                                    <path
                                        stroke-linecap="round"
                                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                                        d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z"
                                    ></path>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            Unlimited Content Updates <span
                                class="text-base-content/75 font-light block"
                                >◦ Managed growth</span
                            >
                        </dt>
                        <dd class="mt-2 text-base/7 t">
                            Your business never stops evolving, and neither
                            should your website. Your 12-month partnership
                            includes managed updates, ensuring your content
                            stays fresh and your tech stack remains
                            cutting-edge. Whether it's a new service launch or a
                            quick text change, we handle the code so you can
                            focus on running your business.
                        </dd>
                    </div>
                </dl>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

